ote><br />\n<br />\n好似唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />閒日去睇吓先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能有緣相見</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇個日記住出post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話時話香港既博物館畀唔畀影相?<br />\n英國博物館一般都可以影.唔知道所以問定先,<br />\n如果唔畀就唔帶相機了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去歷史博物館試過影冇人阻止 我諗唔開閃光燈就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd66bd2046427b2dff7d4ba133aef04aeaeda20","tid":382284,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢排有咩展覽睇？同埋有冇咩博物館推介</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主去睇呢個 睇落幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.timable.com/zh-hk/exhibit?q=exhibition#/event/1428172\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.timable.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fexhibit%3Fq%3Dexhibition%23%2Fevent%2F1428172&d=v%2BAlg%2BW9BTXNfQ5RjVNRLQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=22b6b09f\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.timable.com/zh-hk/exhibit?q=exhibition#/event/1428172</a><br />\n<br />\n其他展覽<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.timable.com/zh-hk/exhibit?q=exhibition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.timable.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fexhibit%3Fq%3Dexhibition&d=v%2BAlg%2BW9BTXNfQ5RjVNRLQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c0e0cfe0\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.timable.com/zh-hk/exhibit?q=exhibition</a></blockquote><br />\n真心唔該曬你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係香港博物館列表 有排你去 希望樓主搵到獨處嘅樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m