.org/zh-hk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%25A4%25A8%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8&d=v%2BAlg%2BW9BTXNfQ5RjVNRLQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4057ec40\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adc03eb1ba08fa12812ee2c599fbcefd4f253c6","tid":382284,"uid":54736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:10:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去歷史博物館試過影冇人阻止 我諗唔開閃光燈就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n盡量都唔開閃,一般博物館室内都夠光,<br />\n只係驚唔畀影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n影應該唔會唔比掛"},{"pid":"c3c197cc179912277dad8f98571ed5d8c583d0ae","tid":382284,"uid":1545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"睇書"},{"pid":"1662e3daef3d9b2461bd88cb7e5819d032107478","tid":382284,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:29:48.000Z","msg":"影相<br />\n<br />\n打桌球，保0<br />\n<br />\n跑步<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行山就唔好自己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba32937b6a01c76762f6aad9ac2a83f48fac5f69","tid":382284,"uid":105501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:34:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我去歷史博物館試過影冇人阻止 我諗唔開閃光燈就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n盡量都唔開閃,一般博物館室内都夠光,<br />\n只係驚唔畀影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n影應該唔會唔比掛</blockquote><br />\n其實一般嘅展物都可以影相㗎<br />\n但有啲展覽係講到明所有展品都唔可以影相<br />\n通常入場嗰時都會講明<br />\n又或者係有啲展物大部分都可以影相<br />\n但零零舍舍有一，兩幅展品係唔可以影相<br />\n<br />\n利申：得閒都會去博物館hea下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}